{"tid":39898,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】【冒死生B】病媽分娩 16醫護助平安產女","createTime":"2016-12-15T00:04:48.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T00:25:57.000Z","uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"514fb329b8080513a48decabb55414da90fc78e9","tid":39898,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T00:04:48.000Z","msg":"片:<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161215&amp;guid=56047052&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161215%26guid%3D56047052%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&d=E9yJEMmn1VVTMm8ooIaxqxpDoU409oZNeObLMRtCPuc%3D&h=ffb3adc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20161215%26guid%3D56047052%26category_guid%3D10793096%26category%3Dinstant&h=bf380408\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20161215&amp;guid=56047052&amp;category_guid=10793096&amp;category=instant</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/15/080358_f1788be85fcda1e440bf792b1b02d58a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F15%2F080358_f1788be85fcda1e440bf792b1b02d58a.jpg&h=d78f038f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/15/080358_497d6d2914b61260e459359179fc2346.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F15%2F080358_497d6d2914b61260e459359179fc2346.jpg&h=cf2cb7d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5R7G7xq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5R7G7xq.jpg&h=2d71a65e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(更新影片)<br />\n<br />\n湖南永州產婦李伶俐(化名)，7年前誕下兒子後，體重由55公斤(約121磅)增至90公斤(約198磅)，今年初懷上第二胎後，體重飆升至280斤(約308磅)，睡覺不能自己翻身，生活幾乎不能自理。前日(13日)近中午12時，湖南省人民醫院產科醫生緊急開會，出動產科、麻醉科、新生兒科等共16名醫護人員，為這名「肥媽」接生，順利誕下一名9.1磅的女嬰。<br />\n<br />\n由於只有1、2名醫護人無法撐起孕婦的體重，多名醫護人員排起「接力隊」，一人負責前排麻醉，後面的醫生護士用力頂着，支撐孕婦身體，讓麻醉科醫生為其進行全身麻醉。產科醫生透露，該名「肥媽」在入院時即明確診斷：患有嚴重子癇，高血壓，妊娠糖尿病，心臟擴大、心功能3級，肺動脈高壓、肺炎、肺水腫、低蛋白血症，代謝綜合症、以及睡眠窒息症，屬於極高危產婦。<br />\n<br />\n「肥媽」的種種症狀，對於麻醉醫生來說也是極大的挑戰。因為常用的穿刺針只有8厘米，硬膜外麻醉成功率非常低。如果實施全身麻醉，就像一場賭博，因為孕婦頭頸短粗，並有睡眠窒息症，全身麻醉可能引致缺氧。而手術後拔喉，呼吸管理也是一大難題。一旦出現缺氧，將嚴重威脅產婦及胎兒的生命安全。<br />\n<br />\n最終，醫院產科主任姚穂率領團隊，從孕婦體位、穿刺部位、到生命體徵的檢測，再到氣管的維護等，經過2個多小時的手術，「胖媽」終於平安誕下女兒，所有醫護人員都汗流浹背，但感到非常高興。<br />\n<br />\n《今日女報》/《長沙晚報》"},{"pid":"a8328d8143491e5f662383e33ffeeeddea5f8d50","tid":39898,"uid":2567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T00:15:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">時鐘同肥芝愛的結晶</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"949f11d882158e958f4760263099472140359ccf","tid":39898,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T00:16:39.000Z","msg":"9.1 磅 bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b6d8732d1cf6e33c60137e43567c8e96496f0d7","tid":39898,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T00:17:04.000Z","msg":"嘩 咁都插得入"},{"pid":"7ee970a86f078e6cceb563fbc79d0c7b8230ee41","tid":39898,"uid":5812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T00:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}